    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We certainly will fail time after time."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "At times we’re too ashamed to turn again,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just stop and breathe yourself out on the Lord,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And breathe Him in. (Proclaim: “Oh, Lord!“)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When there’s no rest in me, He is my rest."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When there’s no peace around, His peace is best."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We know Him through His word, the Spirit brings"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Reality."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Present your body, in His presence stay."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s faithful and adept all to arrange."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s writing His own history today,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Give Him the way. (Proclaim: “Lord, today!“)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s always there to give us what we need."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our oldness turns to newness—He’s the Spring!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He turns our deadness to enlivening"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By dispensing."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So put your introspective mind at ease,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He calls us, “Look away and feast with Me!”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Don’t try to analyze so many things."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Love and believe. (Proclaim: “Yes, we believe!“)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So call on Him, your open spirit bring,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not busy with so many outward deeds."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His Body’s rich supply and covering"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Will guard our being."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Don’t be afraid to give yourself to Him."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Remaining whole and guarded, we miss Him."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Body’s life supply the members bring,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "While opening. (Proclaim: “We open, Lord!“)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I need the other members; they need me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We take the loving way excellingly."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His love is the unique enduring thing"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To make us Him."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    }
